ase and a positive net-debt position.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/commercial/smartworks-secures-major-lease-in-pune-with-wolters-kluwer/125382683?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-38542/125382683.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "commercial"}]}